description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Reception/Administrator lead Emergency Services.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full time 37.5 hours per week&lt;/strong&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Band 4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;A rewarding opportunity has arisen in our Emergency department for a highly motivated and enthusiastic reception lead. You will need to show good leadership skills and to be able to maintain an excellent line of communication between the Reception team and Management team. You will also be first point of contact for patients, visitors and other Health care Professionals, and will receive them in a professional and courteous manor. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Previous supervisory experience is desirable but not essential although sound overall administration &amp; IT skills are required along with a positive and enthusiastic approach.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You are required to have excellent Customer Service skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidate will need to be highly motivated team player, who shows good flexibility and careful attention to detail providing patients with a high quality service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are a 24 hour service and flexibility is essential in supporting the teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holder will provide a range of administrative support to the Reception team and management team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We pride ourselves on being a friendly positive team who are customer care focused and work closely together under pressure. If you like a fast paced atmosphere then we would love to hear from you. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
